entries.femaleVariant: What're you still digging for?! C'mon, let's get outta here.
Chill. I got a new knee, got me runnin' like a fuckin' gazelle now.
Hand-me-down, from my brother. He got some fancy reinforced model.
So he finally remembered you exist, huh? Last time the gonk pretended he didn't even know you.
Well, that was when he was lunching with his boss. Then he fucked up some big project, now nobody wants to eat with him.
Yeah... corporats are like the bomb squad. Only mess up once. Anyway, get those gazelle legs pumpin', let's delta.
